<HEADLINE> Death Toll in Nairobi Blast Tops 247: Official </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NAIROBI, August 12 (Xinhua) -- The last figure of death toll
in Friday's Blast in Nairobi topped 247, Brigadier John Waweru,
official responsible for the rescue work, told Xinhua Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
He said the casualties reached 5,047 in all and that 4,572 had
been discharged after treatment in hospitals. There are 260
people who are now admitted at hospitals and seven of them are
critical, he added.
</P>
