they had found 200 corpses and that 14 were on Tuesday night. He
told Xinhua that only one people has been saved alive under the
rubble since the rescue work began last Saturday.
</P>
<P>
He asserted that the rescue work would end immediately as
there is no glimpse of hope of finding any one alive later.
